query:
INSERT INTO programs (universityId, cityId, iscedDetailedFieldId, nameEn, nameCn, degreeType, language, tuitionPerYear, currency, admissionRequirements) 
SELECT 
  u.id,
  (SELECT id FROM cities WHERE nameEn = 'London' LIMIT 1),
  (SELECT id FROM isced_detailed_fields WHERE code = '0412' LIMIT 1),
  'Master of Business Administration',
  '工商管理硕士',
  'master',
  'English',
  25000,
  'GBP',
  'Bachelor degree, GMAT/GRE'
FROM universities u WHERE u.nameEn = 'Imperial College London'
UNION ALL
SELECT 
  u.id,
  (SELECT id FROM cities WHERE nameEn = 'London' LIMIT 1),
  (SELECT id FROM isced_detailed_fields WHERE code = '0613' LIMIT 1),
  'Master of Computer Science',
  '计算机科学硕士',
  'master',
  'English',
  22000,
  'GBP',
  'Bachelor in CS or related field'
FROM universities u WHERE u.nameEn = 'Imperial College London'
UNION ALL
SELECT 
  u.id,
  (SELECT id FROM cities WHERE nameEn = 'Zurich' LIMIT 1),
  (SELECT id FROM isced_detailed_fields WHERE code = '0714' LIMIT 1),
  'Bachelor of Engineering',
  '工程学学士',
  'bachelor',
  'English',
  18000,
  'CHF',
  'High school diploma'
FROM universities u WHERE u.nameEn = 'ETH Zurich'
UNION ALL
SELECT 
  u.id,
  (SELECT id FROM cities WHERE nameEn = 'Zurich' LIMIT 1),
  (SELECT id FROM isced_detailed_fields WHERE code = '0521' LIMIT 1),
  'PhD in Physics',
  '物理学博士',
  'phd',
  'English',
  0,
  'CHF',
  'Master degree in Physics'
FROM universities u WHERE u.nameEn = 'ETH Zurich'
UNION ALL
SELECT 
  u.id,
  (SELECT id FROM cities WHERE nameEn = 'London' LIMIT 1),
  (SELECT id FROM isced_detailed_fields WHERE code = '0412' LIMIT 1),
  'Master of Finance',
  '金融硕士',
  'master',
  'English',
  28000,
  'GBP',
  'Bachelor degree, GMAT'
FROM universities u WHERE u.nameEn = 'The London School of Economics and Political Science';
